rows.label: xs12140100_MSG0001
rows.name: Luxaar... His memories... They are part of me, now...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12140100_MSG0002
rows.name: When he dissolved...he became one with the protoplasm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12140100_MSG0004
rows.name: I see now the reason why they feared the Samaarians.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12140100_MSG0005_2
rows.name: the Samaarians created new lifeforms to serve them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12140100_MSG0007
rows.name: The original Ganglion were synthesized...they're artificial.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12140100_MSG0008
rows.name:
Which is why they fear humans...
the descendants of their creators![ST:wait ]
